lore: Lich Overseers are able to move their scythe-shaped staff with great dexterity and speed. When they see an ally trying to flee during a raid, there is no warning â€” just a flash of silver followed by a head rolling on the ground to their feet. The last thing the deserter will see is an Overseer's boot crushing their skull.
menagerieDialog: I'll sleep when I'm dead.\n\nWhich happens to be right now. Good night!
You are far too merciful on your subjects. Punishment breeds obedience, and you'd do well to learn that fact.
Knowledge is power, and I have a lot.
We must seek out the Necronomicon. With it, my true power will be realized.
name: Lich Overseer
